<p><rs xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" type="person" ref="bio.xml#_1925">Bernhard van Meurs</rs>, <ref target="biblio.xml#lit_604">‘Avondwolken’</ref>. Van Meurs 1877, p. 164. Translated from <rs xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" type="person" ref="bio.xml#_841">Ludwig Uhland</rs>.</p>
